The paper discusses the security of smart mobile networks and the development of novel security technologies, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions vulnerabilities in the core network and complementary access methods, which are related to network security (cs.NI) and system and information security (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the collection and analysis of information about cyber-attacks, which falls under the category of cybercrime (cs.CY). Finally, the paper mentions the goal of improving mobile network security, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
